== 續集 ==
《地心冒險3：飛向月球》繼續由原班人馬出演。2014年8月時，劇組人員宣佈本劇的兩位編劇{{link-en|凯莉·海斯|Carey Hayes}}跟{{link-en|查德·海斯|Chad Hayes (writer)}}已着手編寫續集的劇本<ref>{{cite news|title='Journey' Sequels in the Works With 'Conjuring' Writers (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/journey-3-4-works-conjuring-725651|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-08-14|language=en|access-date=2016-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826151314/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/journey-3-4-works-conjuring-725651|archive-date=2016-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，本劇的兩位製作人[[布萊德·派頓|布萊德·派頓]]跟[[巨石強森|巨石強森]]會為續集分別導演及尋找演員<ref>{{cite web | url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/brad-peyton-mature-journey-3/ | title=Brad Peyton Wants A More "Mature" Journey 3 | work=wegotthiscovered.com | accessdate=2015-06-09 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525032419/http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/brad-peyton-mature-journey-3/ | archive-date=2015-05-25 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後再有宣佈續集不只一集，而是會有兩集<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dwayne-johnson-journey-3-4-writer/|title=Dwayne Johnson Journey 3 and 4: Writers Hired For Two More Sequels|work=Slashfilm|access-date=2016-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011192034/http://www.slashfilm.com/dwayne-johnson-journey-3-4-writer|archive-date=2016-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年1月，地心3的计划被证实已取消。<ref>{{cite web|author1=David Stephens|title=Dwayne Johnson Confirms That Journey 3 Isn’t Happening|url=https://screenrant.com/dwayne-johnson-journey-3-cancelled/|website=ScreenRant|accessdate=2018-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180429024538/https://screenrant.com/dwayne-johnson-journey-3-cancelled/|archive-date=2018-04-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

